      <title>As Defense Pressures Rise, so Must the Budget</title>
      <category domain="https://www.newsdeeply.com/arctic/geopolitics-security/">Geopolitics &amp; Security</category>
      <category domain="https://www.newsdeeply.com/arctic/governance/">Governance</category>
